title: Kumanek
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Beer/Wine, European, Ukranian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Ukranian atmosphere, serving Ukranian, Moldovian, Russian, and European cuisines with a small selection of vegetarian meals and changing vegan options. Staff speak (some) English; menu is in English and Russian. Find traditional variations of porridge, polenta (ask for with red sauce only), borscht & baked potatoes. Has a non-smoking room. Note that you must pay by their own special currency that you can exchange for nearby. They have wifi for free.
